ver-</div><div class="t m80b x20 he y1a2b ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ance of those who have patiently waited for </div><div class="t m10f4 x20 he y1d07 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">His coming and whose names are written in </div><div class="t m1331 x20 he y1785 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the book of </div><div class="t m42e x95 h21 y1785 ff6 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">life.&quot;—The Great Controversy, </div><div class="t m13ab x20 he y14f8 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">page 634. </div><div class="t m9d1 x8 h1 y1d5e ff1 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Joyous Reward of the </div><div class="t m3ed xa0 h1 y1b08 ff1 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Redeemed </div><div class="t m286 x70 he y1a04 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">8. </div><div class="t m116d x7b he y17c0 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What is said of the wilderness </div><div class="t md2c x20 he y1b1a ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and the solitary place? Isa. 35:1. </div><div class="t mb31 xbc he y1a31 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Nom.—This text has reference primarily </div><div class="t m34b x58 he y191b ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to new-earth conditions. However, it may </div><div class="t m8a7 x58 he y14fe ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">also have a spiritual application to the pres-</div><div class="t m223 x58 he y1aa1 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ent as in the following quotation: &quot;There </div><div class="t m19f9 x58 he y219d ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">are places which are now a moral wilderness, </div><div class="t m1d31 x33 h5f y23d3 ff4 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">[21</div><div class="t m895 x20 h34 y23d3 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1 </div><div class="t m8d0 x90 h34 y23d3 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
